THE COMPANY BELIEVES THAT IT IS IN COMPLIANCE IN ALL MATERIAL RESPECTS WITH APPLICABLE

ENVIRONMENTAL LAWS AND REGULATIONS. IN 2004, THE COMPANY INCURRED CAPITAL EXPENDITURES OF

APPROXIMATELY $50.2 MILLION FOR ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION FACILITIES. THE COMPANY IS ALSO REMEDIATING ENVIRONMENTAL CONTAMINATION

