TO

ARCOXIA

. THE FDA HELD A HEARING ON FEBRUARY 16-18 TO DISCUSS

SAFETY ISSUES RELATED TO COX-2 INHIBITORS. IN ADDITION, THE CHMP

IN EUROPE IS CONDUCTING A REVIEW OF ALL ASPECTS OF THE

