THAT REVIEW, AS INTERIM MEASURES, THE SUMMARY OF PRODUCT

CHARACTERISTICS FOR COX-2 INHIBITORS WAS REVISED, INCLUDING ADDING

NEW CONTRA-INDICATIONS FOR COX-2 INHIBITORS GENERALLY AND FOR

ARCOXIA

SPECIFICALLY. THE COMPANY IS UNABLE AT THIS TIME TO

PREDICT THE FINAL OUTCOME OF CHMPS REVIEW. THE OUTCOMES OF EACH

OF THESE REVIEWS COULD MATERIALLY, NEGATIVELY AFFECT THE MARKET

POTENTIAL OF

ARCOXIA.

