COUNTRIES IN EUROPE, INCLUDING THE UNITED KINGDOM AND GERMANY, AND

THE COMPANY EXPERIENCED A DECLINE IN

ZOCOR

SALES IN THOSE

COUNTRIES. IN JUNE 2006,

ZOCOR

WILL LOSE ITS MARKET EXCLUSIVITY IN THE UNITED STATES AND THE COMPANY EXPECTS A

DECLINE IN

