FOSAMAX

WAS SET TO EXPIRE IN JULY 2018. MERCK DISAGREES WITH THE DECISION OF

THE COURT OF APPEALS AND HAS REQUESTED RECONSIDERATION BY THE COURT OF APPEALS.

