IN JULY 2004, THE OPPOSITION DIVISION OF THE EUROPEAN PATENT OFFICE RENDERED AN ORAL DECISION TO REVOKE THE COMPANYS

PATENT IN EUROPE THAT COVERS THE WEEKLY ADMINISTRATION OF ALENDRONATE. THE COMPANY HAS APPEALED THIS DECISION;

